tions for future bakeoffs.
    One thing we do not do here is get into the details of specific systems; each of the participants was required to provide a four page description of their system along with detailed discussion of their results, and these papers are published in this volume.
  
  
    The corpora are detailed in Table 1.
    Links to descriptions of the corpora can be found at http://www.sighan.org/bakeoff2003/ bakeoff_instr.html; publications on specific corpora are (Huang et al., 1997) (Academia Sinica), (Xia, 1999) (Chinese Treebank); the Beijing University standard is very similar to that outlined in (GB/T 13715&#8211;92, 1993).
    Table 1 lists the abbreviations for the four corpora that will be used throughout this paper.
